  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2025-06-11",
    "date": "2026-03-30T15:52:47Z",
    "text": "Cross-Boundary Wildfire Solutions Act\n\nThis bill directs the Government Accountability Office to study wildfire mitigation across land ownership boundaries and make recommendations to simplify cross-boundary wildfire mitigation between federal land management agencies and state, local, and Indian tribal governments."
